  "text": "The second more complex test case is inspired by the experiment of [CITATION_1] , who monitored a seawater-freshwater mixing zone over time using AMT. The models at t = 0 and t = 1 are shown in Figs. 4a and 4b. The models comprise a 100 m thick 100 Ωm layer, in which seawater intrusion occurs in the lower 50 m. The aquifer overlies a 630 Ωm half-space.",
